parameters: Quite the challenge, but not a match for me.

Man, I thought we were in trouble, but we managed to defeat
them, huh?

Seriously, you're so reliable. We're gonna get a hefty
reward for this!
Hmph, how petty to be concerned about money.
Not that I'm asking for any, do as you like with it.
Feels kinda bad, y'know? Having you work for free and all.
Plus, on top of that, I get to enjoy your... services.\I[12]

What should I have you do today? I'm looking forward to
it...\I[12]
About that, there's something I want to discuss.
When we return to town, may I come to your house?
That's unusual, isn't it? To have a talk with the captain?

We'll talk in detail at your house. For now, let's hurry
back to town.
